title: Ayoub Boukhari
text:
Ayoub Boukhari (born 6 May 1997) is a Dutch <a href="association%20football">football</a> player of <a href="Morocco">Moroccan</a> descent. He plays for <a href="Sparta%20Rotterdam">Sparta Rotterdam</a> and their youth team.
Club career.
He made his <a href="Eerste%20Divisie">Eerste Divisie</a> debut for <a href="Sparta%20Rotterdam">Sparta Rotterdam</a> on 30 November 2018 in a game against <a href="Helmond%20Sport">Helmond Sport</a> as a 78th-minute substitute for <a href="Gregor%20Breinburg">Gregor Breinburg</a>.
